Package models

Class Project

java.lang.Object
models.Project
public class Project extends Object
This class represents a Project in the system. It contains a list of supervised projects and methods to assign them to students or transfer to supervisors. It also has methods to retrieve and update information about the projects from the database.
Author:
Timothy Lee, Justin Wong, Jun Hao, Lee Cheng Yao, Abhishekh
